content.detailedDescription: I was outside smoking and looked up like i always do at the sky. then seen three trangle shaped crafts above me moving in circles in the sky and they looked like they were moving as one. then shot fast to the north of me and stayed moving around as said before. then i had seen orbs of light commming out of them flying around orbiting around the triangles shot a few beams of light to eachother for about 10 min. and then darted across the sky for about another 40 min. as the trianlge crafts were moving back to me. then the orbs had gone into the triangles and shot fast in the sky upwards and were gone. then four smaller dots blinking and flasing were sitting in the sky for about another 30 min moving sparaticly through the sky and making fast and slow blinking lights and got realy realy bright then dissapered like a ghost in the night and this is not my first sighting i have seen i see them about 3 to 4 times a week and have counted more than 16 crafts in the sky that i know are not planes from my military service that i have done.
content.flightPath: Stationary,Hovering then path,Path with directional change,Path then hovering
content.summary: Watched a triangle craft proturde other crafts out of it and fly around and then gone.

content.detailedDescription: Walking up street toward the north of my house. looked up and saw same pattern of lights as the last 6 craft with a plus or cross of lights of various colors and patterns. i caught sight of it as it passed out of sight going toward the ne wich is a change of direction for this bunch. they seem to picking up the pace on the pass overs of our house.Time of night was a little earlier than usual.
content.summary: 7 th objeect in the last month single craft

content.detailedDescription: I found three frames of this object in the last few seconds of a 30 second video i  took of clouds. i did not see the object. i went into the video to extract images of the clouds and found a sphere moving up through the 3 frames. the first 2 were grey and the 3rd was white and very spherical looking. i am posting the original video and the 3 extracted frames. i can not tell how large or how close it is.
content.summary: Found on video i was taking of pretty cloud. unseen at time of video.

content.detailedDescription: I went outside to smoke a cigarette when, first thing i saw was 6 or so hovering lights in a strange formation flying in perfect synchronization (possibly a single ship) across the sky.  i called my husband outside to witness this event with me.  i live with roommates and do not have the key to the back gate and the lights went behind a tree where we could somewhat still see them as they continued their path sw.  they came to the edge of the tree and then vanished.  we could not see exactly where they went, but we could no longer see them through the tree.
content.summary: Around 6 orange lights in formation fly across sky then vanish

content.detailedDescription: My family and i were on the lake..Been out there all day..We threw out some floats for cat fish around 8pm and headed back to the docks slowly cruising on the pontoon boat. as we can around the bend of one of the bays we could see the lights from the docks ..Just above all the lights there was a small very shiny "star" i said to my son "aw look at that star" we all looked ..Then it got bigger and and bigger..The light was so bright ..But didn't have a beam as anyother light would when shining at night...Then as it came closer tp the boat wr stopped shut the boat off..The light started to dim...Then it came about 30 ft from the boat or less. and hovered for a min or two..The slowly went to the left as it hovered over the water there were pulsating lights of silver tint it wasn't a huge craft but it waz big ..The light was so brighy at the beginning of the sighting it was unreal..It was so close to us and it was transparent or black at the same time ..I think i could see thru it but it was black at the same time..Maybe from the sky i don't know.. it was pretty incredible
content.flightPath: Hovering then path,Path with directional change
content.summary: Triangular aircraft with no noise

content.detailedDescription: I was out for a walk around the corner of my house and i saw a ufo right above telephone wires. it flew a straight path from behind me and then flew and dissapered past my site of the houses in front of me it went about 10 to 15 miles per hour and reminded me of the square ship on the opening credits of starwars. it made a buzzing sound and the craft seemed to have some sort of calming effect on me for some reason.
content.summary: Square ufo 20 feet above telephone wires going 15 miles per hour

content.detailedDescription: I saw and my friend as well two pairs of green and blue lights together like on airplanes, but traveling at extremely fast speeds over the 405 freeway and then over the buildings, it was extremely fast and brightened for a period and then faded in the horizon
content.summary: Two green-blue lights shoot out of control through the sky

content.detailedDescription: I take pictures of the northern lights whenever i can.  on friday april 26, 2013 i went out to see what i could find.  after a few pictures of stars and shooting stars i headed back to the townsite and set my camera up for one last shot.  i have a canon 60d on tripod with a sigma 20mm f/1.8 lens and remote set for a 2 second exposure.  the pictures were taken approximately 5 seconds apart.  i saw this light in the sky and snapped a photo, 5 seconds later i snapped another but it appeared to be going in the opposite direction (180 degrees) and then in the next picture it was gone.  at two second exposure it was moving pretty slow compared to a shooting star which would cross an average of half of the view with this lens.
content.summary: Light moving south to north and change direction 180 degrees in 5 seconds.

content.detailedDescription: I was coming up my stairs to my home. i have a clear view of catalina island. i heard boat slapping on the ocean and i saw the shape and did not recall seeing a boat like that so i snapped a couple of pictures. when i downloaded them i saw the black object behind the boat.  i felt that the disc was chasing this boat. i don't know why but that is what i felt.
content.summary: A strange boat was going very fast sw the disc behind it

content.detailedDescription:
My friend and i were going to ralphs to pick up some milk. as an avid sky watcher i forst noticed them while driving. we get to ralphs and park, and see them perfectly. we looked up and saw two giant bright white/orange-yellow lights that didnt flash, almost directly on top of each other. they were not moving. other planes and helicopters were flying around, and they were all tremendously smaller, were all flashing and were moving. out of thin air a third one appeared, it was not cloudy nor was it hidden behind a building, tree, etc. the three than proceeded to make a check mark formation, still remaining just as big and bright and not flashing or blinking, and they seemed to almost teleport into position instead of move. they stayed stationary and hovering for two minutes, all the while other aircraft were flying around them. we had to go in a store for less than a minute, and when we came back there was not a trace of them anywhere. we looked all over the sky and drove around a bit, but did not see them again.

when i first noticed it, i thought it was a helicopter. but it was too big, too bright, not flashing or blinking, and was not moving at all.

i was extremely excited, because i have never seen aircraft make a checkmark position. they were brighter, yet still very high, than anything aircraft i've seen before, and literally did not move. i immediately grabbed my phone and started taking pictures.
content.summary: Three giant white lights in a check mark formation

content.detailedDescription: Me and my girlfriend observed a triangular craft traveling north at a very high rate of speed.  it disappeared from view in a matter of  less than 10 seconds. it was a structural craft that was brightly lit.  we were outside looking at the north star when it flew by.  it was the first that she had seen and the third for me.
content.summary: Triangular craft traveling north

content.detailedDescription: we were (me and my brother)going to home in my car (i was driving the car) when my brother see a small stick alien running (4 mph) in the pavement, he say "what is this", the alien was coming in my car direction, the small alien has 2.3 ft., the entity is small and there are 3 cars in the red traffic sign (stopped), when the traffic sign turns into green i don't wait for nothing putting my car to run faster, i don't know if the small entity was noticed by the other cars.
content.summary: Nightcrawler in brazil

content.detailedDescription: I was having cigarette on balcony in clichy iin the evening and saw an ufo fly from the ne to sw appx.  was similar in size to a boeing 777.  i was scanning the sky and heard a noise so i had noticed it.  my feelings were elated at the time.  i lost sight due to the fact i was done smoking my cigarette and returned inside.
content.summary: Watched object go from ne to sw and ascend into clouds rapidly

content.detailedDescription: I walked out in my backyard to let my dogs out. i saw three or four bright exploding lights directly overhead. high up in the sky. five minutes later. i saw a black cloud or shadow low on the horizon heading my way. i thought it was a low storm cloud. it was dark and hard to see. i watched this cloud or black shadow continue to get closer. i lost sight of it a few times. all of a sudden it was coming over my back yard neighbors house.My dogs started to bark like crazy. all i could see was a black dark shadow. i did not hear any noise other then my dogs barking. when it got over my carport and my next door neighbors house. the street light directly in front of my house came on. it has been not working right for a few months. when the light came on i immediately saw a dull gray object. i thought omg it's a drone. but it had no fuselage or tail. it had no rivets. and was smooth. there were no lights on it at all. i was less then a hundred feet from it. i only saw it illuminated for about four seconds. then i lost sight of it as it passed over the house. i was shocked. i let my dogs in as they were still barking. i got my camera went back outside got on my roof for about two hours. but did not see anything. i could not sleep. i don't understand what i saw.
content.summary: I saw three exploding bright lights high up in the sky.Five minutes later i saw a black cloud heading my way.

content.detailedDescription: My friend looked up at the sky this morning and noticed the sun. had a perfectly circular rainbow around it. he captured it on a digital camera and noticed in the picture the presence of a small white orb just to the right of the sun. it is a clear photo that should be examined further. thank you.
content.summary: This morning over miami, florida a rainbow ring appears around the sun. photo reveals a small light orb to the right of the sun.

content.detailedDescription: My boyfriend and i were driving west on hwy 60 (brandon blvd.)  approx. 7:20 pm around april 25, 2013 we were in some heavy traffic and i noticed the sky was filled with trails and was hazy.  the sky had taken on a milky appearance.  i snapped a pic on my phone and forgot about it.   i have been curious about the jet trails in the sky and sometimes photograph them.  just today, may 13, 2013, i was going through images on my phone and stumbled upon an image that i cannot understand.  look just to the 11:00 hour above the shorter electric pole and zoom in, you will see 4 lights, that look like they are casting shadows.  there is also another light, similar to a crescent just above the brighter lights to the right.  i have no idea what this is and i did not see this in the image when it was photographed...I'm freaking out a little because i had no idea this was on my phone.
content.summary: I discovered this picture on my phone.  about a month ago, april 25ish...My boyfriend and i were driving west on brandon blvd. and i noticed the numerous jet trails in the sky and took a pic.  i am blown away!

content.detailedDescription:
Driving south on 101 i saw an object over rohnert park which appeared round, with red & blue pulsing lights, and lots of little white lights. i saw it from a mile north, down until i couldnt turn my head safely while driving. no place to pull over safely.

i thought it was a ufo at first sight because it was unusual, and stationary. i noticed it as a fixed point, which i drove closer to. upon passing, when i could look to my left to see it directly, it was about the size of a car, hovering in one place, and putting on a light show you'd expect at a rave, not on a flying vehicle. i felt to communicate with it telepathically. my thought was "i can't believe what i'm seeing" and i felt that an impulse came from the object to change my thought around it to "i know what i'm seeing". i was elated and wishing i could stop and look at it without having to drive. i was on a section of freeway where i couldn't pull over safely, so i couldn't stop and film it. i sent the feeling and message of love and peace, thumbs up. my gut feeling is whatever the intelligent source of this vehicle was, is very benevolent.
content.summary: i saw an object over rohnert park which appeared round, with red & blue pulsing lights,lots of little white lights. i saw it from a mile north, down until i couldnt turn my head safely while driving. no place to pull over safely.

content.detailedDescription: I am on the 6th floor of a highrise bldg and sitting on the sofa watching tv. during a commercial i looked outside like i always do. i saw a bright glowing thing up in the sky and jumped up and went close to the window. it was something i've never seen or heard of before. it was quite large considering how far it was from me and hard to explain what it looked like....Could not see a structured vehicle because it was surrounded by a bright orange "glow" like hot coals in a campfire with no flames. i just kept staring at it trying to make sense of it, i didnt even think to grab camera or binoculors. i didnt want to leave the window because i just had to keep watching, i wanted to run tell someone but was afraid it would be gone. all of a sudden the orange glow shut off and i saw a very tiny red dot move away extremely fast heading west. it disappeared so fast it left me feeling shocked. i felt very afraid and closed my drapes. it was there for about 10 minutes while i was looking at it, i dont know how long it was there before i noticed it. i have never before seen anything in the sky,only planes, jets, helicopters,etc. i was shook up for hours afterwards. i found this website while trying to find out what i saw and if anyone else saw it. i think i'll keep a camera handy from now on.
content.summary: An oval/oblong shape that was very bright orange like hot coals just hovering in the sky.

content.detailedDescription: I was looking out of my landing ( top of the stairs ) window with my son, feeling a bit anxious as i don`t like thunder storms.I live in a place called cwmbran (south wales), and the orbs seem to come down close to pontypool. there was a lightning strike at the same time as the 3 orbs came down, my son and i saw it, i shouted to my partner to come upstairs, but by the time she got to the top of the stairs the orbs had gone back up at exactley the same angle, but had changed colour. they were probably bigger than a car. it took about 45 seconds for them to come down and go back up i think. the thing that sticks in my mind is the change of colour from white to red/orange. i dwelled on calling the police for a while, but after thinking about trying to explain it, i changed my mind. not long after a police helicopter over newport ( very close to cwmbran ) chased a ufo. not much was said about it in the local papers. i`m only a normal person and cannot really guess because of the distance, but i would probably say that they were travelling over 500 mph (very unsure though) but they were very fast. hope this helps.
content.summary: 3 orbs came down at 45 degree angle. white on the way down, orange or red on the way up.

content.detailedDescription: It was a very clear night so my family, wife, child, and i went out stargazing with some of our telescopes. we live in chino california about 36 miles east of los angeles so out light pollution and smog doesn't give us the best night sky views, but due to high temperatures and a light breeze the moisture and smog were all but gone and besides fighting the light pollution it was a particularly clear night. great views of the crescent moon, saturn, and jupiter, i am an astronomer with my masters degree in astrophysics, i hold a b.S. degree in aviation science, and a a.S. degree in air traffic control. i am very active in tracking passing satellites, the iss as well as other low earth orbit objects that can readily be seen with the naked eye or a decent pair of binoculars. so after our great night of gazing we packed up and headed for home, after getting all of the gear safely back into the house i stopped for one more to gander at the sky to take in just how amazingly clear the stars were it was 10:28pm, and i noticed two very bright blue/white stars that seemed misplaced around -2 magnitude. they were located near arcturus and were not part of the bo���tis constellation. as i watched them  for about 2 min. they dimmed down to about -0.5 magnitude and quickly started in the north eastern direction, their distance apart from each other did not fluxuate and they dimmed and started motion at the exact same time. it took them roughly 3 min. to disappear in the ne horizon. in comparison the iss takes roughly 10 mins to clear horizon to horizon, at 290 miles up and 17,000 mph. these two objects appeared to be higher up than that and moving about 3 times as fast. i use an app on my phone called satellitear which will show very accurate locations of any potentially visible satellites. the two objects in question did not match the locations of any publicly known satellites or iridium flares. i am a man of science and i like logical explanations for things, and this occurrence is above what i can personally classify. i am very interested to see if anyone else saw this occurrence it was rather astonishing to witness. i wish i had my equipment still set up because all my recording devices were packed away in the house at that time. i didn't feel or hear anything outside of the normal region that i live in.
content.summary: Two very bright objects, hovering then flying away to the ne in formation.

content.detailedDescription: Was at sudbury hill salisbury conducting military exercise it was 0300 am and was on sentry had to hand laser range finder thermal sight military grade military grade nvgs(night vision googles ) it was a clear night and was looking all around at the stars was amazing view when i noticed an airliner then all of a sudden thee was an object next to the air liner at first i thought it was a satellite but i have witnessed ufos before all over the works and since i was a boy so no stranger to this phenomenm the object was a bright sphere and moved with speed it quickly overtook the airliner i could not get an accurate reading on the laser range finder i watched with nvg and thermal imager follows it across the sky for about 5 min it then went 90 degrees very fast and then just disappeared .. i was amazed its been a while since i had a sighting
content.summary: White object observed near airliner

content.detailedDescription: We first saw one about just over a week ago. they look like stars but then they start getting brighter then dimmer. they will yhen start flashing red blue and sometimes green lights. we think they must be pretty high altitude because we can see them mive up down and in figure 8 patterns. sometimes there's two or three and sometimes up toten. they usually form random patterns but once they made a circle and lately they have been making triangle formations, and different types of triangles. we think they may be drone testing by the air force here, or more. my roommate whith whom i've been watching them with has seen an unmarked white suv going through town with guys dressed up in vests and had pistols holstered in plain view. he saw them at tim horton's and persued the vehicle to a secluded area of town and ended it. we think the government may be experimenting new technology here, or these crafts may be from another world.
content.summary: Strange blue and red star like ufos seen in north bay ontario canada

content.detailedDescription:
At approx. 9pm on saturday, a group of 6 including me were relaxing in our hot tub when  the person next to me saw the object. when it came into my view, it was an orb the color of a strong fire. there was some flickering but the orange fiery light emitted remained constant through the arced path; despite it's relative direction of travel to us. distance and size was difficult to determine, but i would guess at it being about 1000 ft. up and about the size of a car. the light intensity was approx. the strength of a street lamp at 200ft. distance from us would have been no more than about 1/2 a mile away. it traveled silently at a rate of approx. 5-7 degrees of view per second at it's broadest section of it's arc. lost sight due to distance, trees and other ground obstructions.

there were airplanes noted some time after the event, but it was obvious that what we saw was not an airplane.

everyone was generally excited and giddy over the event though i was likely the most enthusiastic as experiencing an event like this was on my bucket list.

the object returned 2-3 hours later from the same direction and arc, but further away, perhaps 5 degrees lower from our perspective and bringing our viewing lower into the nearby trees. a late comer to our gathering observed this second passing and thought they saw a more mechanical blinking rather than a flickering as first observed.

we unfortunately didn't have any recording devices with us; being around water, but i have made an overlay on a map that describes the likely flight path of this object based on where we saw it appear and leave from our position.
content.summary: Flaming sphere flickering arcing path

content.detailedDescription:
On guam, on 12 may, at about 1945 local time (0945 gmt) both my wife and i saw 3 separate, bright (venus bright) red, moving  lights in the western sky.  the 3 lights were at about 15-20 degrees of elevation and about 245 to 260 degrees of azimuth.   they were separated by about 5 degrees of azimuth, at approximately the same elevation, and all three were near the elevation of orion, the moon and jupiter, but approximately 15 degrees south of them.

the objects made no noise that we heard, but moved towards us (to the east) and then made hairpin turns to the wnw and faded into the night sky.   the entire event lasted no longer than about 5 minutes.

we called atcc at both the won pat international airport and anderson air force base.  neither reported seeing anything on their radar during that time period.

one of us is a private civilian pilot and a holder of a ph. d. in oceanography with much experience observing the night sky.  nothing of this nature has ever been seen before by this reporter.
content.summary: 3 separate bright (venus bright) red lights appeared low in the western sky at ~1945 local guam time, approached to the east, stopped, hovered, and made a hairpin turn to the wnw and faded into the night sky.

content.detailedDescription: My roommate and i were on our front porch talking when he yelled hurry turn around, look !!! he then got up quickly and ran  as i was turning and getting up and we saw a really large glowing object in the sky coming down at an angle,it slowed,changed direction a little bit then stop for a second then continued coming down,it was red,orange,yellow glowing and looked like it emitting something then it got lower and disappeared. we heard no noises at all .. we were and are really excited about it.
content.summary: Slow moving ,controlled ,glowing ,slowly disappeared
